description:
&lt;p&gt;The Colorectal Department is looking for a motivated Registered General Nurse to support the Straight To Test service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role has been created to support the STT Colorectal Cancer Pathway and help achieve the 28 day Faster Diagnosis Standard. It requires the nurse to be part of the busy nursing service and STT Clinical Lead. It involves assessing patients referred to the service and arranging necessary investigations to support earlier diagnosis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holders will be required to have a sound knowledge of the Gastro Intestinal anatomy and the ability to communicate appropriately by telephone, assessing patient’s needs. Communication with the wider team and community services will be a prominent role within this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in this post please contact below for further discussion:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trushma Patel, CNS on 01895 279391 trushma.patel@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameTrushma PatelJob titleCNSEmail addresstrushma.patel@nhs.netTelephone number01895 279391&lt;/p&gt;
